                            <comment id="14151525" author="jajans" created="Mon, 29 Sep 2014 09:19:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;For completeness, my reply on this on the Felix-dev ML:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m less inclined to immediately state this as a bug. Though it is by convention to use port 443 for secure HTTP, actually nothing prevents me from using port 80 instead for secure HTTP.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</comment>
